  "body": "### Description\r\nShandong testnet is PoS from the begining but the transition mechanism is still fired, particularly overriding the _evmBuilder_ with the Paris definition.\r\n\r\nAs a workaround for syncing Shandong these lines can be removed\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/hyperledger/besu/blob/2cafa8a25d27ee302a4e42a9769eada9f800e7d9/consensus/merge/src/main/java/org/hyperledger/besu/consensus/merge/MergeProtocolSchedule.java#L65-L68\r\n\r\nbut this cannot be applied in general because it will break ETH-Mainnet consensus\r\n",
